<HEADLINE> Ragtime Star Files Civil Rights Suit  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
    NEW YORK (AP) -- A Broadway star has filed a lawsuit over his arrest and
detention by the New York Police Department.
</P>
<P>
	   Alton Fitzgerald White, 35, who stars in "Ragtime" as a black musician
harassed by white firemen, has filed a civil rights lawsuit alleging false
